Leave the top-right corner for manual logo placement.
TEXT: Headline: "Embrace New Beginnings Together!" Subhead: "Celebrate the Chinese New Year with us." Microcopy: "Reflect on the past, look forward to opportunities."
SCENE: A vibrant, festive environment showcasing diverse individuals (at least 5) of varying ethnicities, wearing traditional Chinese attire (like qipaos and tang suits), joyful expressions, holding lanterns and decorations celebrating the Chinese New Year. The background should include subtle elements of the festive decorations, such as banners and fireworks in soft focus.
COLORS: Predominantly white backgrounds with accents of red for a festive touch; main red (#FF0000) for the CTA; light gray panels for benefit boxes.
TYPE: Use Montserrat sans-serif font; bold uppercase for the headline; clear, readable subtext in dark color for contrast.
CTA: Join Us in Celebration
LOGO ZONE: Top-right corner reserved with empty space for logo placement.
READABILITY: Ensure strong hierarchy with high contrast; large text; safe margins; no text over busy areas.
RENDER: High-quality rendering with clear facial expressions, subtle shadows, and bright colors.

QC: logo zone empty, CTA verbatim, no brand name unless allowed, mobile-readable

NEGATIVE:
Do not render any logo/brandmark/wordmark/watermark. 
Do not include any text inside the logo zone, including the word "Logo". 
Do not add any brand/company name text unless explicitly allowed by brand system. 
Do not change the CTA text in any way (no paraphrase, no quotes). 
Do not include clutter, low contrast, tiny text, or busy background behind text. 
Do not produce low-resolution images, artifacts, distorted faces/hands, or uncanny anatomy. 
Do not add watermarks, mock UI, random signage text, or extra unreadable text blocks.
